Dialogue: 1,0:00:09.15,0:00:12.97,Main - Italics,Stage director,0,0,0,,Five minutes to curtain up. \NAll sections, get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:18.83,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Koko—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:19.33,Main,Yae,0,0,0,,Kokona-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:23.86,Main,Yae,0,0,0,,Let's make this a great opening night!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:27.62,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Th-That's my line!\NI c-can't wait to perform together!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.35,0:00:32.38,Main,Yae,0,0,0,,No need to worry. Just think \Nabout how much we rehearsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:33.76,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.46,0:00:36.88,Main,Yae (Genie),0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.15,0:00:39.84,Main,Yae (Genie),0,0,0,,Trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.60,0:00:43.45,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Okay.
