Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.05,0:02:25.46,Main,Kathrina (Sultan),0,0,0,,Ah, tonight is the full moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.46,0:02:30.83,Main,Kathrina (Sultan),0,0,0,,Let us enjoy this Arabian \NNight to our heart's content!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.64,0:02:37.25,Main,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,I'm Aladdin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:38.80,Main,Sasuga (Leila),0,0,0,,I'm Leila.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:42.17,Main,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,This time, I want you \Nto know who I truly am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:47.19,Main,Sasuga (Leila),0,0,0,,Yes, no more lies. I want to \Nget to know the real you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:54.81,Main,Panda (Abdullah),0,0,0,,I order you, Genie of the Lamp!\NMake me the sultan of this kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:05.65,Main,Niizuma (Genie),0,0,0,,My wish is for you to be happy, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:07.02,Main,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,But this isn't over!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:10.80,Main,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,I'll become the master of \Nthe lamp once more, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:16.60,Main,Niizuma (Genie),0,0,0,,Aladdin. This time, you're going \Nto grant my wish, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.29,0:03:20.90,Main,Niizuma (Genie),0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:54.60,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,It went great, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:55.43,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yeah.
