Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:06.54,Main,Audience 1,0,0,0,,Kathrina-chan was so cool as the sultan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:09.44,Main,Audience 2,0,0,0,,Sasuga-san was so pretty as Princess Leila!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:12.18,Main,Audience 3,0,0,0,,Panda-chan was so perfect as the villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:16.94,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\b1\fs10\shad0\3c&HE7E9E9&\c&H262234&\frz341.8\pos(154.667,264.134)}Individual Photos 330 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:14.09,Main,Audience 1,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go buy some merch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:15.97,Main,Audience 2,0,0,0,,Great idea! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:21.44,Main,Audience 1,0,0,0,,What?! Yae-chan's photos are all sold out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:23.69,Main,Staff,0,0,0,,We're terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:30.24,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:31.73,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:35.55,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Oh, Shizuka-chan. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:39.30,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Kokona, can we talk for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:43.41,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Sorry! I promised Yae-chan I'd \Npractice some songs with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:46.19,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,But tell me what you thought \Nof the show later!
