Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:57.69,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\shad0\bord0\fs18\an1\c&H17191B&\pos(174.934,281.2)}Private rehearsal
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:01.44,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,I see you made it through the first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:03.49,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Hiiragi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:05.38,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Thanks for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:08.94,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Um... How was the performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:14.87,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:18.39,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Continue practicing the fundamentals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:19.97,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:28.69,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,It was all so new yet so nostalgic
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:34.66,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,We were dreaming the same dream
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:38.65,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Faint memories, predictions of the future
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:44.04,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,We lived through the same time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:47.54,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Every time I hope that something will change
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:53.40,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,I just keep getting more scars
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:06:00.95,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,So I went ahead and just cast \Nmy eyes down coldly again
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:06.03,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,My time of imprisonment had passed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:11.22,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,And you patted me on the head
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:17.15,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,I wanted to keep believing in this light
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:18.69,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1360,1)\fnImpact\fs20\shad0\bord0\c&HF1F7FD&\pos(323.2,287.6)}Coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:21.05,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,So I kept trying to hold these tears back
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:25.27,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,You are the first person (Who brought this)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:25.28,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\b1\fs14\shad0\c&H040202&\3c&H3E393C&\frx356\fry330\frz355.1\move(413.866,303.6,344.533,301.467)}Become a World Dai Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:28.21,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Sun-colored future with you \N(Where) did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:30.60,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,It's like magic
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:35.45,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,We can be honest\N(Our bluff unravels in the wind)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:41.94,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Even this season where our way \Nhome is fragrant feels dear to me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:43.95,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Faint memories, predictions of the future
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:49.29,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,The sign that we're spending \Nthis time together
