Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.22,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:18.20,Main - Italics,Niizuma,0,0,0,,I have to go help out at a charity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:22.49,Main - Italics,Niizuma,0,0,0,,We don't have a show today, \Nso please get plenty of rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:23.94,Main - Italics,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Yae.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:31.94,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Shizuka-chan still hasn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:38.80,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Shizuka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:43.66,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Where are you, Shizuka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:47.42,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:51.90,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,G-Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:53.00,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:56.88,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Um... Has Shizuka-chan been by?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.88,0:15:58.34,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:02.74,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,I actually haven't seen \NOshizu-chan for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:04.69,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:06.85,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks.
