Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:52.60,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I can't find her anywhere. Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:56.04,Main,Audience A,0,0,0,,You should totally see \NSIRIUS's {\i1}Arabian Nights{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:17:00.02,Main,Audience B,0,0,0,,Yae Niizuma-chan is wonderful as the Genie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:00.79,Main,Audience A,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.03,0:17:03.27,Main,Audience C,0,0,0,,Who's playing Aladdin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:05.91,Main,Audience A,0,0,0,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:08.42,Main,Audience B,0,0,0,,It's some new girl... Who was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:10.40,Main,Audience C,0,0,0,,You two are awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:13.64,Main,Audience A,0,0,0,,Oh, who cares? As long as \Nwe get to see Yae-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:16.79,Main,Audience B,0,0,0,,It honestly doesn't matter who's \Nplaying the other role anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.79,0:17:19.31,Main,Audience A,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! And Yae-chan's song was totally...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:34.30,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Kokona?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:36.46,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Kathrina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:38.98,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Oh, u-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.38,0:17:45.83,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,You're not going to use it... are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:49.33,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:57.63,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Why did you want to join SIRIUS, Kokona?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:58.45,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:18:01.19,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure I told you before,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:04.56,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,but I joined SIRIUS\N to become a World Dai Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:08.86,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,That's why I have no intention \Nof losing to you or Niizuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:13.86,Subtitles,Sign,0,0,0,,Keep your head up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:16.07,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:19.99,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,You're the star! If you don't \Nknow what to do as the star...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:24.38,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,we can't support you in support roles,\Nno matter how hard we try!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:27.60,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Kathrina-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:30.56,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Not to mention,\Nwhen you play a lead at SIRIUS,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:33.38,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,you're one step closer \Nto becoming a World Dai Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:37.01,Flashback - Italics,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You can do it too, Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:41.91,Flashback - Italics,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I'll make you shine brighter\Nthan anyone as an actor...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:44.90,Flashback - Italics,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I'll make you into a World Dai Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:47.95,Flashback - Italics,Kokona,0,0,0,,A World Dai Star...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:57.82,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I made a promise with Shizuka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.63,0:19:02.90,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Kathrina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:04.92,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:07.16,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:10.06,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.63,0:19:24.44,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I need to do my best, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:34.43,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Oh, Shamo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:38.81,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,Shh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.18,0:19:43.35,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! Um, have you seen Shizuka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:47.89,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:49.61,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Oh, but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:51.76,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:54.35,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:20:02.72,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,When I'm watching you, it reminds \Nme of how Noa used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:05.62,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,You mean Hiiragi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:10.59,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,Whenever it came to the plays,\Nshe'd try to do everything herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.59,0:20:12.81,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,unable to see what was going on around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:17.22,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,She doesn't seem like that, does she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.22,0:20:18.35,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,She doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.64,0:20:24.49,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,Noa's Sense allows her to see all of \Nan actor's skills and where they excel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.40,0:20:26.94,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.38,0:20:32.25,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,She chose you two for that role because \Nshe knew you could handle the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:34.84,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Us... two?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:40.51,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,Yes. She knew that you and \NShizuka-chan could handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:49.08,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,Senses come alive on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:12.20,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Shizuka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:15.10,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:20.82,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I went off and did what I wanted \Nto do without even hearing you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:27.17,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,But I still want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:30.54,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,With you, I want to become...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.11,0:21:34.58,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,a World Dai Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:44.08,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Took you long enough, Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:51.44,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Let's go back over the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:53.23,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.98,0:21:56.68,Main,Shizuka and Kokona,0,0,0,,So that we can play...
